# <type>: <subject>
# │         │
# │         └─ Short summary (imperative, no period, ≤ 50 chars)
# │
# └─ feat | fix | docs | style | refactor | perf | test | build | ci | chore | revert
#
# <body>  (optional, wrap at 72 chars, explain what and why, not how)
#
# <footer>  (optional — BREAKING CHANGE, Closes #N, Ref #N)
#
# ── Examples ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# feat: add user authentication
# fix: resolve NPE when user payload is null
# docs: update API endpoint references
# refactor: extract validation into dedicated service
# test: add unit tests for OrderService
# chore: bump express from 4.18 to 4.19
#
# breaking: change auth token format
#
# BREAKING CHANGE: old tokens signed with HS256 are no longer accepted.
# All clients must rotate to RS256 tokens before upgrading.
#
# Closes #42
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
